Patch Set 3: Code-Review+1

@Sylvain, currently the start-app.sh does not handle the certificate file copy correctly for non-root user. According to Seshu, there is an open bug for the start-app.sh to make the ONAP user to run SO. when you fix, please make sure the certificates copy from the /app/ca-certificates to the /usr/local/share/ca-certificates directory properly. 
This code depends on the start-app.sh fixes.

